com.github.redhatqe.polarize.metadata

Annotation Type TestDefinition


  • @Repeatable(value=TestDefinitions.class)
 @Target(value=METHOD)
 @Retention(value=RUNTIME)
public @interface TestDefinition
    Annotation to generate an XML file useable by the WorkItem Importer project.

    The MetaProcessor will examine any method annotated with @TestDefinition in order to generate the mapping between a test method in the source code, with the TestDefinition TestDefinition and Requirement ID. This mapping will then in turn be inserted in a post-processing step with the junit report file.

    Since we are using the @Repeatable meta annotation, this is only useable on a JDK 1.8+.

    Example Usage:
